data.description: Welcome home! This spacious home has been updated and beautifully decorated.  First floor offers gleaming hardwood floors, updated bathroom and large eat in kitchen with 42 inch cabinets, recessed lighting and high end stainless steel appliances.  Finished basement with huge family room and additional bedroom.  Large laundry room with extra storage. Fenced yard and 2.5 car garage. Located on a quiet tree line street with nice neighbors and an excellence block club. Seller is willing to leave the furniture in the basement and furniture on main level is negotiable. Home warranty is included.  Sold as-is.
